# exoplanet-analysis
The main repo used for my side-project to find exoplanets using Warp10 and TensorFlow.

# Other repos

* [kepler-lens-ansible](https://github.com/PierreZ/kepler2warp10-ansible), the ansible role to deploy kepler-lens
